10:02.202 --> 10:04.935
- I did what I had to do.
It wasn't personal.

10:04.971 --> 10:06.171
- It felt personal.

10:06.206 --> 10:09.073
- Ben...

10:09.108 --> 10:11.309
I have kids.

10:11.344 --> 10:13.244
