10:25.525 --> 10:27.792
Where is travis, mary?

10:27.827 --> 10:30.428
Where is he?

10:30.463 --> 10:32.663
- I don't know.

10:32.699 --> 10:35.099
- Did you kill him?

10:35.134 --> 10:38.036
